    <step order="2">Define FilterState interface (activeFilter, setFilter, clearFilter)</step>
    <step order="3">Create FilterStateProvider component</step>
    <step order="4">Create useFilterState hook for consumers</step>
    <step order="5">Wire chart DrillInteraction to setFilter</step>
    <step order="6">Add clear button that calls clearFilter</step>
    <step order="7">Create unit tests</step>
